{"tid":862391,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有咩令到你咁掛住前任","createTime":"2018-10-14T19:35:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-15T03:02:05.000Z","uid":131980,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6919ca27870c980c4bf0a3f639deebe5d8e976e0","tid":862391,"uid":131980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T19:35:10.000Z","msg":"講緊係好既掛住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係記仇既掛住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪呢堆字<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n1:自己仆街<br />\n2:失去才後悔,後悔才懂得珍惜<br />\n3:付出太多<br />\n4:好愛佢<br />\n5:欠你太多<br />\n6:仲未搵到新盤<br />\n7:你值得被再次擁有<br />\n8:只記得美好回憶,差既無咩印象<br />\n9:近排開始轉涼,想有個人溫暖下<br />\n10:好似咩都無哂<br />\n11:唔習慣,仲未適應<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0503fba7cacddcc6482f11f02fb35c545a2c237f","tid":862391,"uid":214482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T19:38:43.000Z","msg":"輸比佢個現任（條件上）<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n輸到連車尾燈都見唔到呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13ecd5b3adbab82f3bcff8b6e4a1b2f1a69d24c3","tid":862391,"uid":140336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T19:43:50.000Z","msg":"比較"},{"pid":"af674d6b91df38b2935e529d2428771967ba379a","tid":862391,"uid":151664,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T01:56:21.000Z","msg":"因為鳩痕。 <br />\n唔好懶情深 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  自己一霜情願去掛住人 對方只會覺得你好嘔心 只加想逃離你"},{"pid":"e3cad387d11b14041210bb91f220a0b35dc98fb9","tid":862391,"uid":65429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T03:02:05.000Z","msg":"得唔到咪愛<br />\n<br />\n男人不壞女人不愛<br />\n女人不愛男人不愛<br />\n<br />\n試下俾你好易得到佢 仲邊會愛"}]}